name: Disgraced (itch) (L Kenny)
description:
This is a part of a Snow White's story remake.

Here she's called Malina and is guarded by two gnomes who's left alive. Their names are Rokh and Daba (you may recognize Grumpy and Dopey).

In this part the princess meets the Queen's hunter named Ozen and tries to think for herself, which is quite hard for her.
